{"tid":1054593,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"北韓軍人衣櫃私藏大量錄入BTS歌曲和韓劇OST USB　被警察逮捕拷問","createTime":"2019-03-10T02:32:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-10T06:07:30.000Z","uid":9573,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0dbe228cae18f4336482c6135d34390afdac3eed","tid":1054593,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T02:32:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/1552130083-9c2fbd5fc28cd6b6c77a41e2a631e21d-696x523.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F1552130083-9c2fbd5fc28cd6b6c77a41e2a631e21d-696x523.png&h=498f115e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲北韓人也超愛BTS。<br />\n<br />\n南韓夯團BTS防彈少年團近年紅遍全球，就連北韓民眾也被此韓流感染，根據《Daily NK》報導，一戶住家遭突襲時，發現3張CD跟2個USB，其中一個USB內更裝滿BTS的歌，以及韓劇OST，該USB持有者立即被捕，帶到拘留所審問。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/BBUA1VA.img?h=511&amp;w=799&amp;m=6&amp;q=60&amp;o=f&amp;l=f&amp;x=853&amp;y=461\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FBBUA1VA.img%3Fh%3D511%26w%3D799%26m%3D6%26q%3D60%26o%3Df%26l%3Df%26x%3D853%26y%3D461&h=18712539&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據報導，上月農曆春節期間，政府突襲職業軍人的家中檢查時，發現衣櫃藏有裝滿大量BTS的歌曲，以及韓劇OST的USB，內容還包括電視劇《一起生活吧》以及電影等影片，相關持有人等7名均被逮捕關進拘留所，自上月聯賽盃失冠後，車路士谷底反彈，不同戰線豪取三連勝，北韓政府認為，這行為已違反「侵害社會主義文化」，必須嚴謹拷問並懲處。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/BBUiqJy.img?h=450&amp;w=799&amp;m=6&amp;q=60&amp;o=f&amp;l=f&amp;x=755&amp;y=329\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FBBUiqJy.img%3Fh%3D450%26w%3D799%26m%3D6%26q%3D60%26o%3Df%26l%3Df%26x%3D755%26y%3D329&h=bdf6f2ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n報導指出，若未經許可，不得將其他國的照片、書籍、電影、音樂等帶入北韓，經查發現嚴重將判刑1年，但BTS在北韓相當受歡迎，粉絲為了不被查到，皆以「你最近有背防彈背包沒？」表示最近有在偷聽BTS的歌。"},{"pid":"f93104cdf54cb212765fc57b68188f79aca1c856","tid":1054593,"uid":23170,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T02:39:33.000Z","msg":"如果入面係迪士尼歌曲會唔會即刻連升幾級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b2f1e04d1060208eb759ddfd48413a033fcab28","tid":1054593,"uid":9766,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T02:46:56.000Z","msg":"自上月聯賽盃失冠後，車路士谷底反彈，不同戰線豪取三連勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0483327cc18bbae510ad5399f4dfed19b44854e","tid":1054593,"uid":5267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T05:53:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f9a87fd6e7e8f00d995a9f48b107a0323e85c1a8","tid":1054593,"uid":195627,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T06:07:30.000Z","msg":"車路士谷底反彈，不同戰線豪取三連勝，北韓政府認為，這行為已違反「侵害社會主義文化」"}]}